external_references.description: Secureworks Counter Threat Unit Research Team. (2022, August 17). DarkTortilla Malware Analysis. Retrieved November 3, 2022.

objects.description: [DarkTortilla](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S1066) can detect debuggers by using functions such as `DebuggerIsAttached` and `DebuggerIsLogging`. [DarkTortilla](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S1066) can also detect profilers by verifying the `COR_ENABLE_PROFILING` environment variable is present and active.(Citation: Secureworks DarkTortilla Aug 2022)
